	(2,1,'2013-09-04 13:36:02','2013-09-04 13:36:02','<h2>Car Service NYC &amp; New York\r\nLimousine Service</h2>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Legends Limousine Service will reliably deliver you to your destination in style and on time.  As an industry leader among New York’s transportation services, we’ve built up our reputation over the past 20 years by offering some of the best customer service in the tri-state area and beyond.  Our specialty is on-time transportation throughout New York, New Jersey, and Connecticut, but we’re happy to drive you to all surrounding states.  We’re also a leader in affordable transit to and from all major area airports including JFK, LaGuardia, Newark, Westchester, Teterboro, and Islip.  We use advanced, convenient dispatch technology to expeditiously reach our clients, and our easy-to-use personal and corporate accounts make payments and reservations a no-brainer. </td>\r\n<td>Most important, customer safety is Legends Limousine’s top priority.  All of our 100-plus vehicles and trained drivers are fully licensed and insured.  With our sterling safety record, maintained over 20 years of service, you can travel with us with total peace of mind.  Our drivers are consummate professionals — courteous, experienced behind the wheel, and efficient.  While Legends Limousine is known for its airport transportation services and 24-hours-a-day, door-to-door availability, we offer chauffeur services for all your needs. Whether it’s a business function, your teenager’s prom, or even your wedding, let Legends Limousine get you there.  Both New York City locals and out-of-towners perennially come to us, for our affordable rates combined with unparalleled service.  And with a varied fleet of cars at your disposal, you can choose from late model luxury vehicles (for that special evening) and stretch limousines, to understated town cars.  We look forward to showing you how different travel can be, with the right car and an exceptional driver.  </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Home','','publish','open','closed','','home','','','2014-06-23 15:39:59','2014-06-23 15:39:59','',0,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/?page_id=2',30,'page','',0),
	(4,1,'2013-09-04 13:47:58','2013-09-04 13:47:58','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2013-09-04 13:47:58','2013-09-04 13:47:58','',2,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(5,1,'2013-09-04 13:48:35','2013-09-04 13:48:35','Legends Car Service’s reputation is built on being the tri-state area’s most efficient, reliable airport pick-up and transfer service.  Whether you’re going on vacation or just getting into town, your arrivals and departures will be made infinitely simpler thanks to our punctuality and commitment to customer care.  Traveling with a group? No problem. Our fleet of vehicles, which includes cars, vans, buses, and limousines (all manned by experienced, professional chauffeurs) will ensure that you reach your destination securely.  All you need to do is give our customer representatives your flight details, and we’ll handle the rest.  Our drivers will meet you in the arrivals lounge (look for the “meet & greet” sign) or curbside, according to your preference, to assist you to your waiting car.   \r\n\r\n<strong>Legends Covers the Following Airports:</strong>\r\n\r\n1. John F. Kennedy Airport (JFK)\r\n2. Newark Airport (EWR)\r\n3. LaGuardia Airport (LGA)\r\n4. MacArthur Airport (ISP)\r\n5. Teterboro Airport (TEB)\r\n6. Westchester Airport (HPN)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Arrange for an Airport Pick-Up:</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Call us anytime — we are conveniently open twenty-four hours a day, seven days a week — to make an advanced booking with our reservationists. \r\n\r\n2. Go online and choose the “Online Reservation” option.\r\n\r\n3. Call us when you arrive, for an immediate pick-up.  (Please note that this is the less preferred option; getting a car this way will be based  upon availability.)\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Airport Pick-Up Methods:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Inside Pick-Up (Meet &amp; Greet):</strong>\r\nOur chauffeur will wait for you in the baggage claim area inside the terminal (for domestic flights) or at the customs exit (for international flights).  The driver will be carrying a LEGENDS sign with your name on it.  He will assist you with your luggage and escort you to your vehicle, in the nearest parking lot.\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Outside Pick-Up (Curbside):</strong>\r\nUpon making an advanced reservation, you will receive a confirmation number. We will monitor your flight through our state-of-the-art computer system, confirm its arrival, and dispatch the car to the airport area accordingly. Upon collecting your luggage, call our toll free number, 1(888)LEGENDS (534-3637). Give our operator your name or confirmation number, and our dispatcher will provide you with the car number and direct you to the designated limousine pick-up area. Barring unforeseen circumstances, you should meet your driver within five minutes of making the call.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Airport Procedures and Policies:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Inside Pick-Up (Meet and Greet)</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Your flight will be monitored and confirmed.\r\n2. A car will be dispatched in advance.\r\n3. Your driver will be waiting for you by the baggage claim area (for domestic flights) and at the custom exit (for international flights) holding a LEGENDS sign with your name on it.\r\n4. If you can’t find your driver inside, please call 1 (888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637. Passengers leaving without calling will be charged.\r\n5. It is the passenger’s responsibility to notify us if your flight is changed or if you miss your flight.\r\n6. Cancelation must be at least two hours before arrival time for LGA, JFK, or EWR airports and three hours for TEB, HPN or ISP airports.\r\n7. Passengers are not responsible for flight delays however we are not responsible for airlines updating their arrival times.\r\n8. Complimentary waiting time is provided as follows: 30 minutes from the arrival time on all domestic flights\r\n45 minutes on all international flights\r\n\r\n<strong>Outside Pick-Up (Curbside)</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Flights will be monitored and confirmed.\r\n2. A vehicle will be dispatched in advanced and on stand-by for you at the airport.\r\n3. Upon collecting your luggage call toll free 1(888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637, give your confirmation or your name and legends’ dispatchers will direct you to a curbside point located right outside your terminal where you will meet your driver within a few minutes.\r\n4. If you do not call us to meet your driver after 45 minutes, we will try to contact you on the telephone number provided. If we still fail to reach you, the car will be dismissed and you will be billed for a “No Show”.\r\n\r\n<strong>*Please note when reserving a stretch limo, a suv, or 13 pass van, the inside pick up is the only option available.* </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>*Please note that a credit card is required for all airport pick-ups to secure your reservation and it is your choice whether to use the card for payment at the end of the trip or you can pay cash. Legends will obtain an authorization approximately 25% above the estimated quote to cover any additional charges such as: waiting time, additional stops, gratuity, tolls, etc. Also please note, if you are using a debit card, there will be a temporary hold of the estimate quote plus 25% for approximately three to five business days until the actual charge is processed. </strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Contact us from the airport:</strong>\r\nMain Line: 1(718)788-1234\r\nToll Free: 1(888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637\r\nToll Free: 1(800)788-2119','New York Airport Limo Service','','publish','open','open','','new-york-airport-car-service','','','2014-06-23 15:41:43','2014-06-23 15:41:43','',0,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/?page_id=5',29,'page','',0),
	(6,1,'2013-09-04 13:48:35','2013-09-04 13:48:35','At Legends Car Service we\'ve built a reputation for excellence by delivering the area\'s most efficient and reliable airport pick-ups.  From arrivals to departures, your travel experience will be defined by our commitment to quality customer care and punctual service.  No matter what your transportation needs, we can supply cars, vans, buses or limo services through our trained staff of professional chauffeurs that will reach any airport destination safely and securely. Simply provide our customer representatives with your flight details and leave the rest to us. Depending on your preference, our professional drivers are available to meet passengers in the arrivals lounge (meet &amp; greet)or curbside upon arrival while assisting you to our vehicle to ensure the finest transportation service available.\r\n\r\n<strong>Legends Covers the Following Airports:</strong>\r\n\r\n1. John F. Kennedy Airport (JFK)\r\n2. Newark Airport (EWR)\r\n3. LaGuardia Airport (LGA)\r\n4. MacArthur Airport (ISP)\r\n5. Teterboro Airport (TEB)\r\n6. Westchester Airport (HPN)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Arrange for an Airport Pick-Up:</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Simply call us anytime; we are conveniently open twenty-four hours a day seven days a week, to book an advanced reservation with one of our professional operators.\r\n\r\n2. Go on line and choose the “Online Reservation” option.\r\n\r\n3. Call us for an immediate pick up on arrival at the airport. (Getting a car: based upon availability *Less preferred option*)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Airport Pick-Up Methods:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Inside Pick-Up (Meet &amp; Greet):</strong>\r\nOur chauffer will go inside the terminal and wait for you at the baggage claim area for (domestic flights) or at the custom exit for (international flights), carrying a LEGENDS sign with your name on it, he will also assist you with your luggage and escort you to the vehicle located at the parking lot.