	(75,1,'2013-09-16 18:03:31','2013-09-16 18:03:31','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2013-09-16 18:03:31','2013-09-16 18:03:31','',2,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(445,1,'2014-06-23 15:39:59','2014-06-23 15:39:59','<h2>Car Service NYC &amp; New York\r\nLimousine Service</h2>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Legends Limousine Service will reliably deliver you to your destination in style and on time.  As an industry leader among New York’s transportation services, we’ve built up our reputation over the past 20 years by offering some of the best customer service in the tri-state area and beyond.  Our specialty is on-time transportation throughout New York, New Jersey, and Connecticut, but we’re happy to drive you to all surrounding states.  We’re also a leader in affordable transit to and from all major area airports including JFK, LaGuardia, Newark, Westchester, Teterboro, and Islip.  We use advanced, convenient dispatch technology to expeditiously reach our clients, and our easy-to-use personal and corporate accounts make payments and reservations a no-brainer. </td>\r\n<td>Most important, customer safety is Legends Limousine’s top priority.  All of our 100-plus vehicles and trained drivers are fully licensed and insured.  With our sterling safety record, maintained over 20 years of service, you can travel with us with total peace of mind.  Our drivers are consummate professionals — courteous, experienced behind the wheel, and efficient.  While Legends Limousine is known for its airport transportation services and 24-hours-a-day, door-to-door availability, we offer chauffeur services for all your needs. Whether it’s a business function, your teenager’s prom, or even your wedding, let Legends Limousine get you there.  Both New York City locals and out-of-towners perennially come to us, for our affordable rates combined with unparalleled service.  And with a varied fleet of cars at your disposal, you can choose from late model luxury vehicles (for that special evening) and stretch limousines, to understated town cars.  We look forward to showing you how different travel can be, with the right car and an exceptional driver.  </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:39:59','2014-06-23 15:39:59','',2,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(76,1,'2013-09-16 18:04:48','2013-09-16 18:04:48','<h1 class=\"text-center title\">Car Service NYC &amp; New York \r\n Limousine Service</h1>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Arriving in style is just the beginning with Legends Limousine service. We deliver on-time transportation backed by the integrity of an industry leader. Our reputation as one of New York\'s premiere transport services has been earned one client at a time over 20 years of superior customer care in the tri-state area and beyond. We specialize in reliable transport throughout New York, New Jersey, Connecticut as well as other surrounding states. New Yorkers who demand nothing but the best at affordable rates have made Legends Limousine one of the most popular transport services for the area\'s major airports including JFK, LGA, Newark, Westchester, Teterboro and Islip. Aside from our cutting edge dispatch technology, clients enjoy the benefit of easy-to-use personal and corporate accounts that offer unparalleled convenience.\r\nCustomer safety is our top priority which is why each of our over 100 vehicles and trained drivers are 100% licensed and insured. With such precious cargo, peace of mind is priceless.</td>\r\n<td>Legends Limousine is proud to boast a sterling safety record and we are backed by more than 20 years of reliable service. Our team of professionals is comprised of courteous chauffeurs with a wealth of experience behind the wheel to ensure that your ride is both efficient and secure.\r\nWhile we specialize in airport transportation, Legends Limousine offers more than just door to door service, 24 hours a day. Our broad spectrum of available services is specifically designed to meet your changing needs throughout the year. From proms to weddings to business functions, Legends Limousine is your partner in quality transportation services. Countless local clients and out of town visitors alike take advantage of our affordable rates around New York City to add that extra touch to a special evening. Our fleet of cars can accommodate a variety of requests, from late model luxury vehicles to a broad spectrum of stretch limousines to suit your tastes. We invite you to contact us today to discover the difference quality makes in your travel experience.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2013-09-16 18:04:48','2013-09-16 18:04:48','',2,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
