	(387,1,'2013-12-17 16:16:36','2013-12-17 16:16:36','At Legends Limousine, you’ll discover the difference that a passion for quality and a commitment to service can make.  Our airport transportation capabilities ensure that every client enjoys an on-time departure and punctual pick up.  Worrying about missed flights or waiting for arriving passengers is a thing of the past when you experience our impeccable airport service in JFK limos.  Whether your needs include drop off or pick up, Legends Limousine is proud to be your partner in reliable transportation services.  There\'s no need to waste time in cell phone waiting lots or squander gas while circling the area\'s numerous terminals.  Let our professional drivers streamline the process with our dedicated airport car services.\r\n\r\nWe service some of the nation’s most in-demand transportation hubs and have earned a reputation for excellence year in and year out through our JFK airport limos.  Other companies promise punctuality but fail to deliver reliable results during rush hour periods or through heavy construction zones.  Legends Limousine is the area’s premiere New York airport limousine service because our drivers are intimately familiar with all the issues affecting your trip.  When timing is important, our passengers can rest assured that their journey to JFK airport will be stress-free and punctual.\r\n\r\nAs one of the country’s most popular flight destinations, JFK Airport is an increasingly complex collection of terminals boasting both international and domestic carriers as well as numerous highway routes that can intimidate and confuse visitors.  Many travelers find it daunting to navigate this maze of buildings and airline hubs successfully without the aid of experienced airport service experts like Legends Limousine.  Our seasoned drivers are trained to deliver quality results every time.  They are backed by the Legends Limousine guarantee and are well-versed in getting clients to their gate in a safe and timely manner.\r\n\r\nDon’t leave your travel plans to chance.  Trust the professionals at Legends Limousine to take the hassle out of flying.  Our JFK limo service is renowned for its accurate and professional results.  Taking into account travel time, traffic, alternate routes and time of day, Legends Limousine drivers consider a multitude of factors when planning your route.  These unpredictable aspects of JFK airport transportation are easily controlled through the experience of our established drivers who put safety and timeliness first.  This attention to detail is what you’ve come to expect from an industry leader and ensures an on time arrival for our valued passengers.','JFK Limousine Service & Car Service','','inherit','open','open','','19-revision-v1','','','2013-12-17 16:16:36','2013-12-17 16:16:36','',19,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/19-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(448,1,'2014-06-23 15:42:07','2014-06-23 15:42:07','<div id=\"homeBottomContentText\">\r\n\r\nOuter borough travel? Not to worry. Legends Limousine is your premiere Brooklyn car service. Our punctuality and performance extends well beyond Manhattan, making us one of New York City’s most well-reputed limousine services. For dependable service from Park Slope to Boerum Hill, Brooklyn Heights to Carroll Gardens, and beyond, be sure to call Legends Limousine first.  \r\n\r\nBrooklyn locals are among our most loyal clients, enjoying our excellent Brooklyn transport services at affordable rates.  In particular, Legends Limousine is among the most established limousine services in Red Hook, Sunset Park, and Fort Greene.  For both personal and corporate use, we offer secure, easy-to-use accounts.  And our superior dispatch technology means we’ll always get to you quickly.  \r\n\r\nThe safety and satisfaction of our clients are Legends Limousine’s chief concerns.  All of our drivers and vehicles are 100% licensed and insured.  No comprehensive Brooklyn car service can match our impeccable safety record and 20 years of experience and seamless service.  Our staff counts the city’s savviest, most experienced chauffeurs, with unmatched knowledge of the tri-state area, among its ranks. Thanks to them, Legends Limousine has enjoyed decades as one of Brooklyn’s most highly regarded car services.  We offer a wide range of transportation services that are specifically designed with you in mind, and we can tailor all your trips to your transportation needs. From special events to corporate travel, Legends Limousine is proud to be your premiere Brooklyn car service. \r\n\r\n\r\n</div>','Brooklyn Car Service','','inherit','open','open','','7-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:42:07','2014-06-23 15:42:07','',7,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(353,1,'2013-12-11 17:20:40','2013-12-11 17:20:40','<h2>Car Service NYC &amp; New York\r\nLimousine Service</h2>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Arriving in style is just the beginning with Legends Limousine service. We deliver on-time transportation backed by the integrity of an industry leader. Our reputation as one of New York\'s premiere transport services has been earned one client at a time over 20 years of superior customer care in the tri-state area and beyond. We specialize in reliable transport throughout New York, New Jersey, Connecticut as well as other surrounding states. New Yorkers who demand nothing but the best at affordable rates have made Legends Limousine one of the most popular transport services for the area\'s major airports including JFK, LGA, Newark, Westchester, Teterboro and Islip. Aside from our cutting edge dispatch technology, clients enjoy the benefit of easy-to-use personal and corporate accounts that offer unparalleled convenience.\r\nCustomer safety is our top priority which is why each of our over 100 vehicles and trained drivers are 100% licensed and insured. With such precious cargo, peace of mind is priceless.</td>\r\n<td>Legends Limousine is proud to boast a sterling safety record and we are backed by more than 20 years of reliable service. Our team of professionals is comprised of courteous chauffeurs with a wealth of experience behind the wheel to ensure that your ride is both efficient and secure.\r\nWhile we specialize in airport transportation, Legends Limousine offers more than just door to door service, 24 hours a day. Our broad spectrum of available services is specifically designed to meet your changing needs throughout the year. From proms to weddings to business functions, Legends Limousine is your partner in quality transportation services. Countless local clients and out of town visitors alike take advantage of our affordable rates around New Yo