	(411,1,'2014-01-09 15:46:15','2014-01-09 15:46:15','With Legends Limousine corporate accounts, you’ll never have to wonder about immediate availability or billing uncertainties. Scores of local clients count on our expertise and reasonable pricing to ensure their timely transportation needs. We deliver convenience and professionalism at every turn with our popular corporate accounts. This service allows our regular clients to enjoy our state of the art, streamlined online reservation system, account management and vouchers. Our corporate accounts are just another example of Legends Limousine’s ongoing commitment to customizing your transportation experience.\r\n\r\nYou’re about to experience the unparalleled convenience and luxury that comes with Legends Limousine corporate accounts. Clients can download the corporate account application and mail it to the address below. Along with your application, please include a photo copy of the following:\r\n\r\n- Front and back of the credit card you’d like to be held on file\r\n- Cardholder’s valid government issued ID.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to serving you regularly. Please contact our Corporate Sales Manager for further information at 1.888.LEGENDS (534.3637).\r\n\r\nDownload Corporate Account Application Here\r\n\r\nMail to the following address:\r\nLegends Car Services\r\n88A 4th Avenue\r\nBrooklyn, NY 11217\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.formstack.com/forms/js.php?1658022-PRIqoGEbTU-v3\"></script>\r\n<noscript><a href=\"https://www.formstack.com/forms/?1658022-PRIqoGEbTU\" title=\"Online Form\">Online Form - </a></noscript>','Apply for An Account','','inherit','open','open','','31-revision-v1','','','2014-01-09 15:46:15','2014-01-09 15:46:15','',31,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/31-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(288,1,'2013-11-20 17:57:48','2013-11-20 17:57:48','If you suspect you have left an item in one of our vehicles, please contact us at (718) 788.1234. If the driver finds the item and can bring it back to you, there will be a surcharge to be paid to the driver at the time of the delivery. The charge is based on the distance between you and the driver at the recovery time. If the driver is not able to immediately return the lost item to you, the driver will bring that item to our office. You can then, contact our customer service department to discuss how you may retrieve that item. You may pick it up from our office located at, 88A 4th Avenue Brooklyn, NY 11217, use messenger service, arrange for FedEx to pick it up, request to have it sent to you by mail, etc. (Not paid for by Legends)\r\n\r\nOr you can fill out and submit our lost and found form on the bottom of this page. We will do our best to locate your lost property and contact you with the status.\r\n\r\nPlease note:\r\n\r\n1. Legend is not liable for lost items left behind in any of our vehicles left by passengers but we will do our best to locate and recover your item.\r\n2. It may take 2-3 business days for us to locate your item and bring it back to our office.\r\n3. Our lost and found department is open Monday through Friday between 9a.m.- 5 p.m.\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"287\" title=\"Lost and Found\"]','Lost and Found','','inherit','open','open','','35-revision-v1','','','2013-11-20 17:57:48','2013-11-20 17:57:48','',35,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/35-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(343,1,'2013-12-11 14:03:52','2013-12-11 14:03:52','Every Spring season, Prom is celebrated as a treasured rite of passage for young people and Legends Limousine service is proud to be there every step of the way. We provide a multitude of cars, SUVs and limousines to choose from so prom partiers will enjoy the most comfortable and stylish ride in the tri-state area. For an event as special as Prom, arriving in style means more than just choosing the right dress. It means getting together with friends in the luxury and comfort of a Legends Limousine vehicle to make the night unlike any other. Impress your date or simply enjoy the luxury of chauffeured driving with our extensive inventory of popular vehicles.\r\n\r\nSurprise your high schooler with a gift that will make their evening secure, fun and memorable with our numerous vehicle choices. They’ll stand out in our fleet of stretch Hummers or bring along a group of friends in our popular stretch Escalade vehicles. From the classic Rolls Royce to the cutting edge Mercedes Benz, we have your Prom needs covered. For parents, Legends Limousine offers priceless peace of mind through our chauffeur services by promoting the safest means of travel on Prom night. With late night celebrations stretching into the evening, reserved transportation is always the best way to ensure your teen will enjoy a safe Prom. They’ll be no need to worry knowing our trained and experienced drivers are behind the wheel.','Your Dream New York Prom Limousine ','','inherit','open','open','','53-revision-v1','','','2013-12-11 14:03:52','2013-12-11 14:03:52','',53,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/53-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
