	(440,1,'2014-05-29 17:34:16','2014-05-29 17:34:16','<h2 class=\"subtitle text-center uppdercase\">RESERVATIONS</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"faq-list\">\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How much time do I need prior to making a reservation?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nLegends recommends that you make a reservation, twenty-four hours in advance to ensure availability, however we can always provide immediate requests. Also hours in advance is usually okay depending on availability and the approximate distance from New York City.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Can I call if I need a vehicle right away?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYes you can. We will do our best to estimate the vehicle time of arrival but, in order to avoid the wait we strongly suggest making a reservation in advance at no additional charge.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>What happens if I don\'t get a callback?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nThe client is responsible for being in the vehicle at the time of pick-up, even if client did not receive a call from Legends. Legends can\'t be responsible for calls which are not going through, or when a client provides a telephone for callbacks that is not working, or that\'s going to voice mail.\r\n\r\nWaiting time charges starts from the scheduled time of pick-up.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How much notice is required to cancel a reservation?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nLegends requests that our customers cancel the reservation in advance as follows:\r\n\r\n<span class=\"underline\">Two Hours for pick-up’s from:</span>\r\n- New York City (five boroughs)\r\n- LGA Airport\r\n- JFK Airport\r\n- EWR Airport\r\n- TEB Airport\r\n\r\n<span class=\"underline\">Three hours for pick-up’s from:</span>\r\n- ISP Mac Arthur / Long Island\r\n- HPN White Plains / Westchester\r\n\r\n<span class=\"underline\">Out of town pick-ups:</span>\r\nWe request the approximate duration of the trip from mid-town Manhattan plus an additional hour for cancellation.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class=\"subtitle text-center uppdercase\">TRAVEL</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"faq-list\">\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How much time should I allow for traveling to the airport?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nThe traffic flow between Manhattan to the airports is unpredictable. Please consult your airline and use common sense when booking your reservation. Add extra time for bad weather, rush hours, and during holidays.\r\n\r\nAverage travel time to the New York City Area Airports in normal circumstances:\r\n<table class=\"table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>From</th>\r\n<th class=\"text-center\">To</th>\r\n<th class=\"text-center\">Travel Time</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Manhattan</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">JFK Airport</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">60 minutes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Manhattan</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">Newark Airport</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">60 minutes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Manhattan</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">LaGuardia Airport</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">45 minutes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>I made a reservation to be picked up at the airport, what should I do once I land?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nIf you request an inside pick-up, (Meet and Greet), please look for your driver at the baggage claim for domestic flights or at the custom exit for international flights, he will be holding a Legends sign with your name on it. For any reason, if you can not find your driver, please call us at (888) 534-3637, so we can connect you with your driver.\r\n\r\nIf you request an outside pick-up, just call us after you have picked up your luggage and a Legends dispatcher will direct you to go outside to meet your driver.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Does Legends provide free waiting time for airport pick ups?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYes. You get 30 minutes free waiting time for Domestic flights and 45 minutes free waiting time for International flights. We check the arrival time with your airline, and change your order to reflect the new arrival time. Your free wait starts from that time.\r\n\r\nIf it takes you longer to retrieve your luggage, or if you come out later than the allotted free waiting time, you will be charged.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Is there an additional cost for Meet and Greet service?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYes. Legends charges $15 more for this service, plus the client pays the parking fee at the airport, because the driver must park his vehicle to go inside the terminal.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How long does it take to get through immigration and customs at JFK Airport or Newark airport?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYou never know for sure how long it takes to get through immigration and customs at JFK Airport or Newark airport, first you\'ll have to clear immigration and depending on how many other international flights have arrived around the same time yours did, it could take just a few minutes or up to 2 hours. Entering the United States with a U.S. passport is faster then a non-U.S. passport.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How many people and how much luggage can I fit into a sedan?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nOur Lincoln town cars accommodate up to four passengers and up to four small-medium size luggage.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Do you charge more for extra luggage?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nThere is no charge for luggage if they fit in the trunk of the car, but there will be a charge of up to $10 per bag if placed inside the vehicle.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>What if I have more than four passengers or more than four pieces of luggage?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYour can always request a mini-van. Our mini-vans fit up to seven passengers. (Please see chart below for passengers and luggage accommodations based on small-medium sized bags)\r\n<table class=\"table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Number of Passengers</th>\r\n<th class=\"text-center\">Number of Bags</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">3</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>6</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">4</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">4</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>4</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">6</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>3</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">6</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>2</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">6</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">8</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class=\"subtitle text-center uppdercase\">Payments and Tolls</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"faq-list\">\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How much should I tip?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nGratuities are at the discretion of the passenger when traveling in a regular sedan or mini-van and that usually ranges between 10-20%.\r\n\r\nCharge accounts, 13 passenger vans, stretch limousines, stretch SUVs and buses are charged a mandatory 20% gratuity.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Who is responsible for tolls and how much are they?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nThe customer is always responsible for paying the tolls. Tolls may vary depending on the route the driver takes. The driver reserves the right to take the best route due to traffic of weather conditions. Here are some approximate toll amounts from Manhattan to and from some airports:\r\n\r\nTo and from JFK: $6.50\r\n\r\nTo and from LGA: $6.50\r\n\r\nTo and from NWK: $14.00\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Can I pay for some one else using my credit card?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYes you can, using one of the following options:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>The best and most convenient way to prepay for a reservation is to use our website online at www.LegendsLimousine.com, click on \'MAKE AN ONLINE RESERVATION\' and when you get to the form of payment, click on \'I WOULD LIKE TO PAY FOR THE TRIP NOW\'.</li>\r\n	<li>If you do not have access to the internet, please call us at (718) 788.1234 and ask for our prepaid fax form. Fill it out, sign it and please fax it back to (718) 422.0220.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n*Please note we may request a copy of the front and back of your credit card along with the matching picture id.*</li>\r\n	<li>You may also stop by our office to prepay all of your reservations at:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n88A 4th Avenue\r\n\r\nBrooklyn, NY 11217\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>What form of payments do you accept?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nWe accept cash, and all major credit cards such as: Master Card, Visa, American Express, and Discover card. We also accept traveler\'s check.\r\n\r\n*Please note we do not accept personal checks or diner\'s club card.*\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How do I get a receipt if I pay cash?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYou could always ask your driver for a cash receipt. If you forget, please call us at (718) 788.1234 to request a copy of your receipt and provide us with your name, telephone number, date of the trip, pick-up location/destination along with your total amount.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>What are your procedures on waiting time and how much is the waiting time charge?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nWaiting time charges may be incurred if passengers arrive late to a pick-up time. A nine minute courtesy is given on all reservations except airport pick-ups, which is 30 minutes free waiting time from the arrival time for outside (curbside pick-ups) and 45 minutes free waiting time for inside (meet and greet pick-ups). Waiting time charges are based on an hourly rate for a particular vehicle. Waiting time charges also apply on all additional stops after the complimentary 5 minutes expire and also apply on all round trips after the complimentary 15 minutes have expired.\r\n\r\nThen you will have to collect your luggage which also can take just a few minutes or can take 15-30 minutes depending on how quickly the baggage handlers get your luggage from the plane to the baggage carousels, then it will depend whether the customs officers wave you through or single you out for further inspection and search your luggage, which once again it can take a few minutes or can take another 15-20 minutes.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How is my credit card charged?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nIf you need to pay by credit card, your card number will be taken at the time of the reservation for authorization purposes only. The amount of the authorization is 25% more then the actual fare to cover for any additional stops, waiting time, tolls, gratuity, etc. Please present the same card to the driver upon pick-up. The driver will then imprint of the card and provide a receipt for the signature. Please take your card back from the driver once you have totaled and signed your receipt. That amount will be charged to your credit card.\r\n\r\n*Please note that it may take drivers up to a week from the date of the trip to bring in your signed receipt to be processed in our office and that is the date that will reflect on your statement NOT the actual trip date.*\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class=\"subtitle text-center uppdercase\">Corporate Accounts</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"faq-list\">\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>How do I open an account?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYou can either do it on our web site, or contact our office at 1-888-534-3637. Or you can e-mail your request <a href=\"mailto:Info@Legendslimousine.com\">Info@Legendslimousine.com</a>\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Can I use my account to reserve on the web site?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nWe encourage you to book your reservations on our web site. If you have a personal or corporate account with us, please contact our office to get a password for your account. And you can use your account for any trip,from anywhere. You always get a copy of your order and a confirmation number when you provide us with your e-mail address. You can also modify or cancel your reservations.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Can I build a profile for future usage?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYes.You can build your own profile by creating a user name and a password for you to login evrytime you need to book a reservation on line After you book your first order our system will let you manage your reservations, preferences, save addresses and contact information, simplifying your reservation process, it also allows you to modify and cancel your reservation.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Is it safe to give my credit card details online?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nAll transactions with LegendsLimousine take place on a secure server using SSL encryption technology to ensure your personal and payment details are protected. To verify that you are shopping in a secure environment, a padlock will appear in your browser. It is normally in the status bar, towards the right hand side, at the bottom of your browser window.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class=\"subtitle text-center uppdercase\">Special Needs</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"faq-list\">\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Does Legends provide infant and toddler car seats?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYes. We can provide you with either a rear-facing infant seat or a forward-facing toddler seat upon request.\r\n\r\n*Please note: Our drivers will gladly assist you in installing the car seats, but please be advised it is your responsibility to make sure they are properly installed.*\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Do you provide wheel chair accessible vehicles?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYes we do. Please call in advance to make a reservation.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>What is your policy on pets?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nLegends gladly accommodates travelers with pets but, please keep the following in mind:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Must notify the operator when you make the reservation so we can accommodate you. If you fail to do so, the driver has the right to refuse transporting the pet.</li>\r\n	<li>All pets must be leashed or in a special carrier when traveling in a car.</li>\r\n	<li>All pets over twenty-five pounds must ride in a mini-van or a van, with the exception of service dogs.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class=\"subtitle text-center uppdercase\">Miscellaneous</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"faq-list\">\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Does Legends Car Service call when my car is on location?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nIn most cases you will receive a phone call from us when you driver arrives. Occasionally we are unable to call all passengers due to heavy call volume.\r\n\r\n*Please note that you are responsible for waiting time charge from reservation time and not from the time we call. Nine minutes free waiting time is given on all reservations as a courtesy.*\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Can the driver go inside the building to bring the luggage out to the car?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nUnfortunately drivers can not leave their vehicles unattended but they will be pleased to assist you with your luggage from the side-walk to the vehicle.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Must I wear a seat belt in Legends vehicles?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nNo. We are for hire vehicles, therefore New York State Law\'s exempt passengers from all seat belt laws, but for your own safety we strongly recommend that you wear your seat belt at all times.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Do you provide larger vans other than seven passenger vans?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nYes. Legends can provide you with a late model passenger van that could accommodate up to thirteen passengers with out luggage. Please see chart for passengers and matching number of luggage (based on small-medium size luggage)\r\n<table class=\"table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Number of Passengers</th>\r\n<th class=\"text-center\">Number of Bags</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>13</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">0</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>12</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">0</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">2</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>10</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>9</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">10</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>8</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">10</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>7</td>\r\n<td class=\"text-center\">14</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class=\"que\">\r\n<h4>Does Legends allow smoking in the vehicles?</h4>\r\n<div class=\"ans\">\r\n\r\nNo. Smoking is prohibited for the driver and the passengers by the NYC Taxi and Limousine Commission. All vehicles must be clean and smoke free at all times. Your chauffeur will be subject to a summons and fine if he lets you smoke in the vehicle.\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>','F.A.Q','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-v1','','','2014-05-29 17:34:16','2014-05-29 17:34:16','',33,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(442,1,'2014-06-03 13:15:21','2014-06-03 13:15:21','At Legends Limousine we always strive to provide the best customer service possible. Our customer service agents are available 24/7 to help you with all your reservation needs and we are happy to assist with any special requests. For immediate assistance, please call 718-788-1234 or toll free 888-LEGENDS (534-3637). You can also contact us via email using the links available below for any questions, comments, requests or feedback. We are always pleased to hear from you.\r\n<table class=\"contactUsTable\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"50%\">\r\n<h3>Headquarters</h3>\r\n<div class=\"hr2\"></div>\r\n<div>Legends Car Services <br>88A 4th Avenue<br>Brooklyn, NY 11217</div></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>Reservations</h3>\r\n<div class=\"hr2\"></div>\r\n<div>To make or change a reservation: From New York City Call 1-718-788-1234 24 Hrs Or Call Toll free 1.888.legends (534.3637)</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Contact Us','','inherit','open','open','','46-revision-v1','','','2014-06-03 13:15:21','2014-06-03 13:15:21','',46,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(446,1,'2014-06-23 15:41:17','2014-06-23 15:41:17','Legends Car Service’s reputation is built on being the tri-state area’s most efficient, reliable airport pick-up and transfer service.  Whether you’re going on vacation or just getting into town, your arrivals and departures will be made infinitely simpler thanks to our punctuality and commitment to customer care.  Traveling with a group? No problem. Our fleet of vehicles, which includes cars, vans, buses, and limousines (all manned by experienced, professional chauffeurs) will ensure that you reach your destination securely.  All you need to do is give our customer representatives your flight details, and we’ll handle the rest.  Our drivers will meet you in the arrivals lounge (look for the “meet & greet” sign) or curbside, according to your preference, to assist you to your waiting car.   \n\n<strong>Legends Covers the Following Airports:</strong>\n\n1. John F. Kennedy Airport (JFK)\n2. Newark Airport (EWR)\n3. LaGuardia Airport (LGA)\n4. MacArthur Airport (ISP)\n5. Teterboro Airport (TEB)\n6. Westchester Airport (HPN)\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>How to Arrange for an Airport Pick-Up:</strong>\n\n1. Call us anytime — we are conveniently open twenty-four hours a day, seven days a week — to make an advanced booking with our reservationists. \n\n2. Go online and choose the “Online Reservation” option.\n\n3. Call us when you arrive, for an immediate pick-up.  (Please note that this is the less preferred option; getting a car this way will be based  upon availability.)\n\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Airport Pick-Up Methods:</strong>\n\n<strong>1. Inside Pick-Up (Meet &amp; Greet):</strong>\nOur chauffer will go inside the terminal and wait for you at the baggage claim area for (domestic flights) or at the custom exit for (international flights), carrying a LEGENDS sign with your name on it, he will also assist you with your luggage and escort you to the vehicle located at the parking lot.\n\n<strong>2. Outside Pick-Up (Curbside):</strong>\nAfter you place an advanced reservation, you will be given a confirmation number. We will monitor your flight through our state of the art computer systems, confirm your arrival times and dispatch the car to the airport area accordingly. Upon collecting your luggage, call our toll free 1(888)LEGENDS (534-3637). Give the operator your confirmation number or your name, the dispatcher will then provide you with the car number and direct you to the designated limousine pick-up area. You will normally meet your driver within five minutes.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Airport Procedures and Policies:</strong>\n\n<strong>Inside Pick-Up (Meet and Greet)</strong>\n\n1. Your flight will be monitored and confirmed.\n2. A car will be dispatched in advance.\n3. Your driver will be waiting for you by the baggage claim area (for domestic flights) and at the custom exit (for international flights) holding a LEGENDS sign with your name on it.\n4. If you can’t find your driver inside, please call 1 (888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637. Passengers leaving without calling will be charged.\n5. It is the passenger’s responsibility to notify us if your flight is changed or if you miss your flight.\n6. Cancelation must be at least two hours before arrival time for LGA, JFK, or EWR airports and three hours for TEB, HPN or ISP airports.\n7. Passengers are not responsible for flight delays however we are not responsible for airlines updating their arrival times.\n8. Complimentary waiting time is provided as follows: 30 minutes from the arrival time on all domestic flights\n45 minutes on all international flights\n\n<strong>Outside Pick-Up (Curbside)</strong>\n\n1. Flights will be monitored and confirmed.\n2. A vehicle will be dispatched in advanced and on stand-by for you at the airport.\n3. Upon collecting your luggage call toll free 1(888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637, give your confirmation or your name and legends’ dispatchers will direct you to a curbside point located right outside your terminal where you will meet your driver within a few minutes.\n4. If you do not call us to meet your driver after 45 minutes, we will try to contact you on the telephone number provided. If we still fail to reach you, the car will be dismissed and you will be billed for a “No Show”.\n\n<strong>*Please note when reserving a stretch limo, a suv, or 13 pass van, the inside pick up is the only option available.* </strong>\n\n<strong>*Please note that a credit card is required for all airport pick-ups to secure your reservation and it is your choice whether to use the card for payment at the end of the trip or you can pay cash. Legends will obtain an authorization approximately 25% above the estimated quote to cover any additional charges such as: waiting time, additional stops, gratuity, tolls, etc. Also please note, if you are using a debit card, there will be a temporary hold of the estimate quote plus 25% for approximately three to five business days until the actual charge is processed. </strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Contact us from the airport:</strong>\nMain Line: 1(718)788-1234\nToll Free: 1(888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637\nToll Free: 1(800)788-2119','New York Airport Limo Service','','inherit','open','open','','5-autosave-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:41:17','2014-06-23 15:41:17','',5,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/5-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(447,1,'2014-06-23 15:41:43','2014-06-23 15:41:43','Legends Car Service’s reputation is built on being the tri-state area’s most efficient, reliable airport pick-up and transfer service.  Whether you’re going on vacation or just getting into town, your arrivals and departures will be made infinitely simpler thanks to our punctuality and commitment to customer care.  Traveling with a group? No problem. Our fleet of vehicles, which includes cars, vans, buses, and limousines (all manned by experienced, professional chauffeurs) will ensure that you reach your destination securely.  All you need to do is give our customer representatives your flight details, and we’ll handle the rest.  Our drivers will meet you in the arrivals lounge (look for the “meet & greet” sign) or curbside, according to your preference, to assist you to your waiting car.   \r\n\r\n<strong>Legends Covers the Following Airports:</strong>\r\n\r\n1. John F. Kennedy Airport (JFK)\r\n2. Newark Airport (EWR)\r\n3. LaGuardia Airport (LGA)\r\n4. MacArthur Airport (ISP)\r\n5. Teterboro Airport (TEB)\r\n6. Westchester Airport (HPN)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Arrange for an Airport Pick-Up:</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Call us anytime — we are conveniently open twenty-four hours a day, seven days a week — to make an advanced booking with our reservationists. \r\n\r\n2. Go online and choose the “Online Reservation” option.\r\n\r\n3. Call us when you arrive, for an immediate pick-up.  (Please note that this is the less preferred option; getting a car this way will be based  upon availability.)\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Airport Pick-Up Methods:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Inside Pick-Up (Meet &amp; Greet):</strong>\r\nOur chauffeur will wait for you in the baggage claim area inside the terminal (for domestic flights) or at the customs exit (for international flights).  The driver will be carrying a LEGENDS sign with your name on it.  He will assist you with your luggage and escort you to your vehicle, in the nearest parking lot.\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Outside Pick-Up (Curbside):</strong>\r\nUpon making an advanced reservation, you will receive a confirmation number. We will monitor your flight through our state-of-the-art computer system, confirm its arrival, and dispatch the car to the airport area accordingly. Upon collecting your luggage, call our toll free number, 1(888)LEGENDS (534-3637). Give our operator your name or confirmation number, and our dispatcher will provide you with the car number and direct you to the designated limousine pick-up area. Barring unforeseen circumstances, you should meet your driver within five minutes of making the call.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Airport Procedures and Policies:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Inside Pick-Up (Meet and Greet)</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Your flight will be monitored and confirmed.\r\n2. A car will be dispatched in advance.\r\n3. Your driver will be waiting for you by the baggage claim area (for domestic flights) and at the custom exit (for international flights) holding a LEGENDS sign with your name on it.\r\n4. If you can’t find your driver inside, please call 1 (888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637. Passengers leaving without calling will be charged.\r\n5. It is the passenger’s responsibility to notify us if your flight is changed or if you miss your flight.\r\n6. Cancelation must be at least two hours before arrival time for LGA, JFK, or EWR airports and three hours for TEB, HPN or ISP airports.\r\n7. Passengers are not responsible for flight delays however we are not responsible for airlines updating their arrival times.\r\n8. Complimentary waiting time is provided as follows: 30 minutes from the arrival time on all domestic flights\r\n45 minutes on all international flights\r\n\r\n<strong>Outside Pick-Up (Curbside)</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Flights will be monitored and confirmed.\r\n2. A vehicle will be dispatched in advanced and on stand-by for you at the airport.\r\n3. Upon collecting your luggage call toll free 1(888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637, give your confirmation or your name and legends’ dispatchers will direct you to a curbside point located right outside your terminal where you will meet your driver within a few minutes.\r\n4. If you do not call us to meet your driver after 45 minutes, we will try to contact you on the telephone number provided. If we still fail to reach you, the car will be dismissed and you will be billed for a “No Show”.\r\n\r\n<strong>*Please note when reserving a stretch limo, a suv, or 13 pass van, the inside pick up is the only option available.* </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>*Please note that a credit card is required for all airport pick-ups to secure your reservation and it is your choice whether to use the card for payment at the end of the trip or you can pay cash. Legends will obtain an authorization approximately 25% above the estimated quote to cover any additional charges such as: waiting time, additional stops, gratuity, tolls, etc. Also please note, if you are using a debit card, there will be a temporary hold of the estimate quote plus 25% for approximately three to five business days until the actual charge is processed. </strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Contact us from the airport:</strong>\r\nMain Line: 1(718)788-1234\r\nToll Free: 1(888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637\r\nToll Free: 1(800)788-2119','New York Airport Limo Service','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:41:43','2014-06-23 15:41:43','',5,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(455,1,'2014-06-23 15:45:08','2014-06-23 15:45:08','From a classic affair to a modern bash, every wedding needs just the right vehicle to complete its particular theme.  Legends Limousine is proud to provide solutions to your pressing wedding transportation needs; with our full, varied fleet, we can put the finishing touch on any ceremony.  For a vintage flourish, our Phantom Rolls Royce and Jaguar models are the perfect ways to arrive in style (and we have a host of other available options).  And no matter which model you go with, you can feel confident that you’re choosing on-time, reliable transportation.\r\n\r\nLeave the transportation to the experts at Legends Limousine. With impeccable service and value-conscious pricing, reliable transportation is the first item future brides and grooms can check off their list when they choose our certified, insured drivers.  We have earned a sterling reputation as one of the region’s leading wedding transportation services, and we invite you to explore the many ways we can add comfort and convenience to your special day.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, we can help you address one of the most common challenges of planning a wedding. Ensuring reliable transportation for friends and family who require airport shuttle service can get tricky. Legends Limousine has 20 years of experience in coordinating the transportation needs of large groups of attendees for both weddings and related events. We provide on-time, comfortable service to transport your guests between the airport, hotel, wedding ceremony, and reception venue, so your special day can run smoothly. With Legends Limousine managing the arrival of guests and family members, you will be free to relax and enjoy the day.  There’s no better gift than that.','New York Wedding Limousines','','inherit','open','open','','61-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:45:08','2014-06-23 15:45:08','',61,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/61-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(456,1,'2014-06-23 15:45:38','2014-06-23 15:45:38','With a Legends Limousine corporate account, you’ll never have to wonder about availability or deal with billing confusion. Our numerous local clients count on our expertise, professionalism, and reasonable prices to fulfill their transportation needs in a timely manner. Our corporate accounts are the quickest route to convenience, from account management and vouchers, to our state-of-the-art, streamlined online reservation system enjoyed by regular clients. Our corporate accounts are just another example of Legends Limousine’s ongoing commitment to offering the best, most customizable transportation experience in the area.\r\n\r\nYou’re about to experience the unparalleled convenience and luxury that comes with Legends Limousine corporate accounts. Clients can download the corporate account application and mail it to the address below. Along with your application, please include a photo copy of the following:\r\n\r\n- Front and back of the credit card you’d like to be held on file\r\n- Cardholder’s valid government issued ID.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to serving you regularly. Please contact our Corporate Sales Manager for further information at 1.888.LEGENDS (534.3637).\r\n\r\nDownload Corporate Account Application Here\r\n\r\nMail to the following address:\r\nLegends Car Services\r\n88A 4th Avenue\r\nBrooklyn, NY 11217\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.formstack.com/forms/js.php?1658022-PRIqoGEbTU-v3\"></script>\r\n<noscript><a href=\"https://www.formstack.com/forms/?1658022-PRIqoGEbTU\" title=\"Online Form\">Online Form - </a></noscript>','Apply for An Account','','inherit','open','open','','31-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:45:38','2014-06-23 15:45:38','',31,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/31-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(457,1,'2014-06-23 15:46:00','2014-06-23 15:46:00','<h3>Business car services NYC experts on call</h3>\r\nAt Legends Limousine, we know how valuable your time is. That’s why we’ve designed our corporate benefits package to specifically address your needs. We’ve optimized the transportation experience to ensure that our corporate services succeed, where other companies have failed. From the initial booking to your departure, your travel needs are simplified and streamlined thanks to our acclaimed automated systems. As a corporate account member, you’ll enjoy:\r\n\r\n- Easy to use and secure online reservation system\r\n- Simplified and personalized account management\r\n- Electronic billing capabilities\r\n- Dedicated hotline and account executive\r\n- Event coordination\r\n- Streamlined voucher system\r\n- Ability to monitor user activity\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.legendslimousine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Legends-Limousine-application.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Apply Now</strong></a>','First Class Corporate Limo Service New York','','inherit','open','open','','29-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:46:00','2014-06-23 15:46:00','',29,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/29-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(458,1,'2014-06-23 15:46:19','2014-06-23 15:46:19','A premiere New York City transportation provider, Legends Limousine is proud to have served the tri-state area for over 20 years. Our trained professional drivers are committed to the highest level of safety, while our customer service representatives provide top tier treatment at every turn. Punctuality and safety go hand in hand at Legends Limousine, and our passengers have come to rely on us in order to travel comfortably and on time. \r\n\r\nAnd with our easy-to-use online reservation system, arriving on time and unstressed is simpler than ever. By prioritizing your convenience, we’ve established Legends Limousine as an industry leader among our valued clients. From large group outings to airport transportation, our trained and licensed drivers are always on hand to make your travel dreams a reality. Our huge client roster turns to our dependable limo service again and again for all their wedding, corporate retreat, and celebratory transportation needs. At Legends Limousine, we guarantee affordable and safe travel, with none of the hassle usually associated with driving in New York.','About Legends Limousine','','inherit','open','open','','44-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:46:19','2014-06-23 15:46:19','',44,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/44-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(459,1,'2014-06-23 15:47:19','2014-06-23 15:47:19','Your family is important and you demand the best in quality safety assurance. That’s why Legends Limousine offers car seats designed specifically for small children to guarantee their transportation security. We understand the needs of growing families and there’s no reason why you shouldn’t have the opportunity to travel with even the youngest members of your family. We pride ourselves on accommodating all client requests to our fullest abilities and ensuring safety through baby seats is a top priority for Legends Limousine\r\n\r\nAs all parents know, versatility is essential. For this reason, Legends Limousine gives you the flexibility you need. All of our vehicles can be outfitted with convertible baby seats in just moments. While safety is priceless, we also understand the importance of affordability. At only $10, adding this device is extremely economical and is the key to keeping kids safe. From rear-facing infant seats to front-facing toddler seats, Legends Limousine is committed to making every ride safe and fun for your little ones.','Family Transportation','','inherit','open','open','','419-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:47:19','2014-06-23 15:47:19','',419,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/419-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
